(87, 'Chettinad Style Prawn Biryani Recipe', '200 grams Shrimps - or prawns,1-1/2 cups Basmati rice,4-5 Shallots,1 tablespoon Ginger - paste,1 tablespoon Garlic - paste,3 tablespoons Fresh coconut - grated,1 teaspoon Green Chilli - paste,1/2 cup Hung Curd (Greek Yogurt),2 sprig Curry leaves,1 cup Sun', 55, 4, 'Chettinad', 'Lunch', 'Non Vegeterian', 'To prepare Chettinad Style Prawn Biryani Recipe, wash and clean prawns well, collect in a bowl and add ginger garlic paste, red chili powder, turmeric, few drops of lemon juice and 2-3 pinch salt. Mix well and marinate for 15-20 minutes.Wash and soak rice', 'https://yellowchilis.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/prawn-biryani-shrimp-biryani-eral-biriyani-in-one-pot.jpg'),
(88, 'Walnut and Flax Seed Trail Mix Recipe With Figs and Honey', '1 cup Walnuts,1 cup Dried Figs,1/3 cup Flax seeds,1/3 cup Honey,1/2 cup Roasted Peanuts (Moongphali),1 teaspoon Cinnamon Powder (Dalchini)', 25, 4, 'Continental', 'World Breakfast', 'Vegetarian', 'To begin making the Walnut and Flax Seed Trail Mix Recipe With Figs & Honey, in a mixing bowl, combine the walnuts,Â figs,Â flax seeds,Â honey,Â roasted peanuts and the cinnamon powder.Â Preheat an oven to 190 degree celsius.Â Transfer theÂ Walnut and Fla', 'https://www.archanaskitchen.com/images/archanaskitchen/1-Author/Shyma_Menon/Walnut_and_Flax_Seeds_Trail_Mix_Recipe_With_Figs_and_Honey-3.jpg'),
