(94, 'Mukhadi Halwa Recipe (Semolina & All Purpose Flour Halwa)', '1 cup Sooji (Semolina/ Rava),3 tablespoons All Purpose Flour (Maida),1 cup Milk - +1/3 cup extra,1 cup Sugar,3/4 cup Ghee', 40, 6, 'North Indian Recipes', 'Dessert', 'Vegetarian', 'To begin making the Mukhadi Halwa recipe, remove 3 table spoons of semolina from one cup of semolina. and replace it with 3 tablespoons of all purpose flour.Â Transfer this mix into a bowl and add milk. Whisk them together and set aside while you begin to', 'https://www.archanaskitchen.com/images/archanaskitchen/1-Author/Easyfoodsmith/mukhadi_halwa.jpg'),
